11 1. Have never been denied admittance to a teacher education
12 program approved by the Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education,
13 the North Central Association of Colleges and Schools and by the
14 Oklahoma Commission for Teacher Preparation to offer teacher
15 education programs, nor have enrolled in and subsequently failed
