17 the program, except those persons who hold a certificate;
18 2. Have on file with the director of teacher education at an
19 Oklahoma institution of higher education a plan for meeting standard
20 certification requirements within three (3) years; and
21 3. Participate in an induction program as required in Section
22 6-195 of this title and have the same duties and responsibilities as
